headline: A Very Costco Christmas Is Good News for the Stock
summary: Santa Claus must be a Costco member—and that is great news for the stock.  Costco Wholesale  released its December same-store sales after the market closed on Wednesday, showing that the warehouse club closed 2025 on a high note.  It was an unusual outcome for Costco, which has risen 150% in the past five years.
